// Vitest Snapshot v1, https://vitest.dev/guide/snapshot.html

exports[`FacilityExtentComponent > should show form values 1`] = `"<cca-wizard-step heading="Extent of the facility" data-testid="facility-extent-form" class="ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><form novalidate="" class="ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><!--container--><netz-page-heading><!--container--><h1 class="govuk-heading-l">Extent of the facility</h1></netz-page-heading><div class="govuk-!-width-two-thirds"><p>Provide information on the activities carried out and the energy used at the facility.</p><govuk-details summary="More information on the extent of the facility"><details class="govuk-details"><summary class="govuk-details__summary"><span class="govuk-details__summary-text">More information on the extent of the facility</span></summary><div class="govuk-details__text"><p>To determine the improvement target for each facility included in an agreement, we need to know:</p><ul><li>the boundary which encloses the land used in connection with the operation of the installation</li><li> the different categories of activities carried out on the site that consume energy, i.e.: <ul><li>eligible</li><li>directly associated</li><li>ineligible</li></ul></li><li>how much of the energy used on site can be included in the eligible facility (the 70% rule)</li><li> whether the eligible facility includes plant carrying out an activity listed in The Greenhouse Gas Emissions Trading Scheme Order 2020 </li></ul><p> The sections of the form below require you to upload the evidence we need to understand the extent of the facility. </p><p>The evidence you provide should be consistent between each of the relevant sections.</p></div></details></govuk-details><h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Manufacturing process</h2><cca-file-input formcontrolname="manufacturingProcessFile" hint="Upload a description of the manufacturing processes that consume energy on the site, ensuring you include all eligible, ineligible and directly associated activities" label="Manufacturing process description" class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-form-group ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><div class="cca-multi-file-upload cca-multi-file-upload--enhanced"><label class="govuk-label" id="l.manufacturingProcessFile" for="manufacturingProcessFile">Manufacturing process description</label><!--container--><!--container--><span class="govuk-hint govuk-!-display-block" id="manufacturingProcessFile-hint">Upload a description of the manufacturing processes that consume energy on the site, ensuring you include all eligible, ineligible and directly associated activities</span><!--container--><!--container--><input type="file" class="govuk-file-upload" accept="*/*" id="manufacturingProcessFile" name="manufacturingProcessFile"><cca-file-upload-list><div class="cca-multi-file__uploaded-files"><!--container--><div class="govuk-summary-list"><div aria-live="polite" class="govuk-summary-list__value cca-multi-file-upload__message"><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__filename"><a target="_blank" class="govuk-link" href="/">manufacturingProcessFile.xlsx</a></span><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__progress"> </span><!--container--></div><div class="govuk-summary-list__actions cca-multi-file-upload__actions"><button govuksecondarybutton="" name="delete" type="button" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-button govuk-button--secondary"> Delete <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">manufacturingProcessFile.xlsx</span></button><!--ng-container--></div></div><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--></cca-file-upload-list></div></cca-file-input><cca-file-input formcontrolname="processFlowFile" hint="Upload a process flow map identifying all the eligible, ineligible and directly associated activities that consume energy on the site and the interactions between these" label="Process flow maps" class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-form-group ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><div class="cca-multi-file-upload cca-multi-file-upload--enhanced"><label class="govuk-label" id="l.processFlowFile" for="processFlowFile">Process flow maps</label><!--container--><!--container--><span class="govuk-hint govuk-!-display-block" id="processFlowFile-hint">Upload a process flow map identifying all the eligible, ineligible and directly associated activities that consume energy on the site and the interactions between these</span><!--container--><!--container--><input type="file" class="govuk-file-upload" accept="*/*" id="processFlowFile" name="processFlowFile"><cca-file-upload-list><div class="cca-multi-file__uploaded-files"><!--container--><div class="govuk-summary-list"><div aria-live="polite" class="govuk-summary-list__value cca-multi-file-upload__message"><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__filename"><a target="_blank" class="govuk-link" href="/">processFlowFile.xlsx</a></span><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__progress"> </span><!--container--></div><div class="govuk-summary-list__actions cca-multi-file-upload__actions"><button govuksecondarybutton="" name="delete" type="button" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-button govuk-button--secondary"> Delete <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">processFlowFile.xlsx</span></button><!--ng-container--></div></div><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--></cca-file-upload-list></div></cca-file-input><cca-file-input formcontrolname="annotatedSitePlansFile" hint="Upload a plan showing the extent of the entire site/eligible facility and highlight areas on the plan where eligible, ineligible and directly associated activities consuming energy are located" label="Annotated site plans" class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-form-group ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><div class="cca-multi-file-upload cca-multi-file-upload--enhanced"><label class="govuk-label" id="l.annotatedSitePlansFile" for="annotatedSitePlansFile">Annotated site plans</label><!--container--><!--container--><span class="govuk-hint govuk-!-display-block" id="annotatedSitePlansFile-hint">Upload a plan showing the extent of the entire site/eligible facility and highlight areas on the plan where eligible, ineligible and directly associated activities consuming energy are located</span><!--container--><!--container--><input type="file" class="govuk-file-upload" accept="*/*" id="annotatedSitePlansFile" name="annotatedSitePlansFile"><cca-file-upload-list><div class="cca-multi-file__uploaded-files"><!--container--><div class="govuk-summary-list"><div aria-live="polite" class="govuk-summary-list__value cca-multi-file-upload__message"><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__filename"><a target="_blank" class="govuk-link" href="/">annotatedSitePlansFile.xlsx</a></span><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__progress"> </span><!--container--></div><div class="govuk-summary-list__actions cca-multi-file-upload__actions"><button govuksecondarybutton="" name="delete" type="button" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-button govuk-button--secondary"> Delete <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">annotatedSitePlansFile.xlsx</span></button><!--ng-container--></div></div><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--></cca-file-upload-list></div></cca-file-input><h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Eligible process</h2><cca-file-input formcontrolname="eligibleProcessFile" hint="Upload a description of the plant or processes in which you carry out one or more activities that are described in the schedule to the sector umbrella agreement. Your description should include any sub-sectors, where applicable" label="Eligible process description" class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-form-group ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><div class="cca-multi-file-upload cca-multi-file-upload--enhanced"><label class="govuk-label" id="l.eligibleProcessFile" for="eligibleProcessFile">Eligible process description</label><!--container--><!--container--><span class="govuk-hint govuk-!-display-block" id="eligibleProcessFile-hint">Upload a description of the plant or processes in which you carry out one or more activities that are described in the schedule to the sector umbrella agreement. Your description should include any sub-sectors, where applicable</span><!--container--><!--container--><input type="file" class="govuk-file-upload" accept="*/*" id="eligibleProcessFile" name="eligibleProcessFile"><cca-file-upload-list><div class="cca-multi-file__uploaded-files"><!--container--><div class="govuk-summary-list"><div aria-live="polite" class="govuk-summary-list__value cca-multi-file-upload__message"><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__filename"><a target="_blank" class="govuk-link" href="/">eligibleProcessFile.xlsx</a></span><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__progress"> </span><!--container--></div><div class="govuk-summary-list__actions cca-multi-file-upload__actions"><button govuksecondarybutton="" name="delete" type="button" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-button govuk-button--secondary"> Delete <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">eligibleProcessFile.xlsx</span></button><!--ng-container--></div></div><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--></cca-file-upload-list></div></cca-file-input><h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Directly associated activities</h2><div formcontrolname="areActivitiesClaimed" govuk-radio="" legend="Are any directly associated activities claimed?" class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-form-group ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><div class="govuk-form-group"><fieldset govukfieldset="" id="areActivitiesClaimed" class="govuk-fieldset"><legend govuklegend="" id="l.areActivitiesClaimed" class="govuk-fieldset__legend"> Are any directly associated activities claimed? <!--container--><!--container--></legend><!--container--><!--container--><div class="govuk-radios govuk-radios--inline"><!--container--><div class="govuk-radios__item"><input type="radio" class="govuk-radios__input" id="areActivitiesClaimed-option0" value="true" name="areActivitiesClaimed"><label class="govuk-label govuk-radios__label" for="areActivitiesClaimed-option0"> Yes <!--container--><!--container--></label><!--container--></div><!--ng-container--><!--container--><!--ng-container--><!--container--><div class="govuk-radios__item"><input type="radio" class="govuk-radios__input" id="areActivitiesClaimed-option1" value="false" name="areActivitiesClaimed"><label class="govuk-label govuk-radios__label" for="areActivitiesClaimed-option1"> No <!--container--><!--container--></label><!--container--></div><!--ng-container--><!--container--><!--ng-container--><!--container--></div></fieldset></div></div><cca-file-input formcontrolname="activitiesDescriptionFile" hint="Upload a description of the activities consuming energy that have a technical connection with, and serve the eligible activities on the site" label="Directly associated activities description" class="govuk-!-display-block govuk-form-group ng-untouched ng-pristine ng-valid"><div class="cca-multi-file-upload cca-multi-file-upload--enhanced"><label class="govuk-label" id="l.activitiesDescriptionFile" for="activitiesDescriptionFile">Directly associated activities description</label><!--container--><!--container--><span class="govuk-hint govuk-!-display-block" id="activitiesDescriptionFile-hint">Upload a description of the activities consuming energy that have a technical connection with, and serve the eligible activities on the site</span><!--container--><!--container--><input type="file" class="govuk-file-upload" accept="*/*" id="activitiesDescriptionFile" name="activitiesDescriptionFile"><cca-file-upload-list><div class="cca-multi-file__uploaded-files"><!--container--><div class="govuk-summary-list"><div aria-live="polite" class="govuk-summary-list__value cca-multi-file-upload__message"><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__filename"><a target="_blank" class="govuk-link" href="/">activitiesDescriptionFile.xlsx</a></span><span class="cca-multi-file-upload__progress"> </span><!--container--></div><div class="govuk-summary-list__actions cca-multi-file-upload__actions"><button govuksecondarybutton="" name="delete" type="button" class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-button govuk-button--secondary"> Delete <span class="govuk-visually-hidden">activitiesDescriptionFile.xlsx</span></button><!--ng-container--></div></div><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></div><!--container--></cca-file-upload-list></div></cca-file-input><!--container--></div><button netzpendingbutton="" govukbutton="" type="submit" class="govuk-button">Continue</button><!--container--><!--container--></form></cca-wizard-step><!--container--><hr class="govuk-footer__section-break govuk-!-margin-bottom-3"><a class="govuk-link" href="/"> Return to: Manage facilities </a>"`;
